subproject.description:
The programme aims to support the implementation of the OECS Economic Union process through:
1. public education inclusive of radio features, to be aired on OECS Newslink and live broadcast of panel discussions on OECS integration and linked development issues such as Citizen Security;
2. support for the development of a framework for the effective and harmonized operation of the social security system within the OECS Economic Union, which will facilitate the free movement principle enshrined within the Revised OECS Treaty.

